og.description: Police detectives did not recover any bullet casings belonging to Jarrell Milton’s weapon. Homicide investigator Sherry King said two other teens — Jamar Milton, 17, and Shuntayvious Primes-Willis, 15 — opened fire and are responsible for the killing of Jamymell Ray, 31.
